room_title: Escape room "Abandoned Schoolroom" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
review: My friends and I did the Abandoned Schoolroom. Two of us already did Escape the Room before and the rest of us were complete beginners. The puzzles were filled with chemistry, math problems, lockers, etc. The manager was helpful with her hints. I had fun eating the candy we found all over the room. In the end, we had a blast and made it out with only 10 seconds left!

room_title: Escape room "Abandoned Schoolroom" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
review: We had a great time last night in the abandoned schoolhouse. It was actually pretty difficult but we enjoyed ourselves with a group of four!

room_title: Escape room "Abandoned Schoolroom" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
review: We had a great time at the Lubbock Panic room. We were in the Abandoned Schoolroom and escaped with 3 seconds left! Tiffany was great and we had a blast! Thanks for a fun time!

room_title: Escape room "Abandoned Schoolroom" by Lubbock Panic Room in Lubbock
review: Abandoned school room was a really cool set up. Felt like a kid again being in that space.
